sql:
SELECT org_id
FROM organization_metrics
WHERE org_metric_total_publications = (
  SELECT MAX(org_metric_total_publications)
  FROM organization_metrics
);

external_knowledge:
- "beacon of influence" refers to the organization with the highest impact in terms of citations;
- "amassed the greatest number of citations" means the organization with the highest total citations;
- "if there is a tie, the one with the highest average citations per year" means that if two organizations have the same total citations, the one with the higher average citations per year is ranked higher.
